name: I bet you can't pass the level
name_original: I bet you can't pass the level
description:
2020/08/08

If you get stucked in level 5, the portal is on top of the map which is hidden on top of the camera.

According to the mobile game ads.......

  1. I'm sure you will turn off AD blocker
  2. I'm sure you can't pass this level
  3. I'm sure you can't figure out the mechanics
  4. I'm sure you can't jump over the gap
  5. I'm sure you can't catch the timing
  6. 99% of people can't pass level 6!
  7. 99% of people can't find the right exit!
  8. 99% of people feels it is so hard!
  9. 99% of people can't get the GOAL!

Controls

Space/Left click: rewind video (in the level)

R: Restart
